WEBVTT

00:01:59.502 --> 00:02:05.363
Think of all the problems
that we're facing at the moment.

00:02:06.347 --> 00:02:07.509
All.

00:02:08.692 --> 00:02:13.131
Chances are that they are rooted
in the productivity crisis.

00:02:15.226 --> 00:02:16.907
Why this crisis?

00:02:18.438 --> 00:02:23.913
Because the basic tenets
about efficiency --

00:02:23.937 --> 00:02:28.748
effectiveness in organizations,
in management --

00:02:28.772 --> 00:02:33.023
have become counterproductive
for human efforts.